title: Josh Richards and Bryce Hall

description:
Social media kings Josh Richards and Bryce Hall are on the pod today to share all the roast jokes that didn't air during the ROAST OF BRYCE HALL.  They also talk about Whitney's leaked nudes, what might get them canceled, and Sway House party drama.
